name: CrossYiffyMix

and Merged them to create this model, liked it so much that I would share it instead of it being for personal use.

Since this was merged with Lawlas, use the boring_e621 embedding though its fine without it. It's a personal suggestion from me

You also won't need a vae as its merged with the vae baked in.

I'll probably make a version where the vae isn't baked in, though its a big maybe.

Some things to be aware of:

It's prone to generate hair that isn't the same color, I suggest adding the color of the fur with the hair, if it somewhat bothers you

It has a hard time generating tails in the right places in behind point of views

Hopefully you enjoy the model, if there are any problems, leave a comment
